      "writtenOn": "2016-06-17T13:12:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "by add two times q0_sub_p0 to itself with saturation, you could avoid going 16b arithmetic and having to interleave left/right and recombine.\n\nv16i8 tmp \u003d __msa_adds_s_b(q0_sub_p0, q0_sub_p0);\ntmp \u003d __msa_adds_s_b(q0_sub_p0, tmp);\ntmp *\u003d cnst3b;\n\nno?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 229,
        "startChar": 17,
        "endLine": 229,
        "endChar": 23
      },
      "revId": "48b62052f5da793b9d2787235918186c14f984a8",
